JOHANNESBURG - The African National Congress (ANC) honoured struggle veteran Winnie Madikizela-Mandela with a musical and artistic celebration on Friday night in Newtown, Johannesburg. The #AllBlackNight event forms part of the governing party's activities leading up to Madikizela-Mandela's funeral next weekend. READ: Honouring Mama Winnie this weekend: what's happening where Among the artists performing were Thandiswa Mazwai and Zahara. #BlackNightWithWinnie #TributeToWinnie #AllBlackWithADoek eNCA